<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q21_v3" title="Q21_v3" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones es equivalente a 
      <m:math>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
      y no tiene raíz en el denominador?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al racionalizar, 4/√2 × √2/√2 = 4√2/2 = 2√2. Esta expresión es equivalente a la original y ya no tiene raíz en el denominador.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:msqrt>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:msqrt>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original vale 4/√2 = 2√2, mientras que esta opción es solo √2. Como 2√2 ≠ √2, no son equivalentes.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al racionalizar, 4/√2 = 4√2/2 = 2√2, no 4√2. Además, 4√2 es el doble de 2√2, por lo que no es equivalente a la expresión dada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La expresión original vale 4/√2 = 2√2. Como √2 ≠ 1, entonces 2√2 ≠ 2. Por eso esta opción no es equivalente a la fracción dada.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso: racionalización del denominador</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la expresión original</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión dada es:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mfrac>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mfrac>
            </m:math>
            <p>Se pide una expresión equivalente que no tenga raíz en el denominador.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Racionalizar el denominador</strong></p>
            <p>Para eliminar la raíz del denominador, multiplicamos numerador y denominador por</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:msqrt>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:msqrt>
            </m:math>
            <p>Como multiplicamos por la misma cantidad arriba y abajo, la fracción no cambia su valor:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>×</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    <m:msqrt>
                      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    </m:msqrt>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:msqrt>
                      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    </m:msqrt>
                    <m:msqrt>
                      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    </m:msqrt>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Simplificar el denominador</strong></p>
            <p>Se cumple que:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    <m:msqrt>
                      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    </m:msqrt>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Simplificar la fracción</strong></p>
            <p>Como</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mfrac>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mfrac>
            </m:math>
            <p>es igual a</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            </m:math>
            <p>resulta:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mfrac>
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                    <m:msqrt>
                      <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                    </m:msqrt>
                  </m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:mfrac>
                <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  <m:msqrt>
                    <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                  </m:msqrt>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión equivalente sin raíz en el denominador es</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                <m:msqrt>
                  <m:mn>2</m:mn>
                </m:msqrt>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>que corresponde a la alternativa A.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>